featured_reviews.review_id: Jama Masjid is the only one big mosque in Angul. It is on NH-55 Mishrapada, Angul. It is a big mosque where 10k people can pray at a time. It has a good location and communication facility. It is near the Women's College Angul. It is near Bazar Chowk. It is a good mosque. It is surrounded by market. Easily noticable in normal traffic.
